data.description: Highly sought after south Venice gem, with so many possibilities! This move-in ready home with roof installed in December of 2019. This split level home offers a large open floor plan upstairs with a living/dining-room / kitchen combo AND a second floor balcony to enjoy the views. Large Master en-suite has a large Master closet. There are two additional bedrooms and a second full bath. The finished downstairs has potential for an in-law suite, game room or bonus room with a dedicated office/den space and with another 3rd bathroom plus interior laundry. This home is situated on a large lot with mature Florida landscaping and a spacious private backyard. In back you’ll find a garden storage shed with electric hooked up and water spigot attached. It could also be used as a tool house workbench. South Venice is a highly popular and sought after community there are no HOA fees, no CDD fees, and no deed or rental restrictions!  It is close to Alligator Creek and only minutes to Shamrock Park and Shamrock Nature Center. With ample concrete paved parking, you can bring your boat or RV. There is also an optional South Venice Civic Association residents can join for ferry access to a Private Beach! So bring your pets and your toys! The home is close to grocery stores, great schools, medical offices, award winning beaches, golf courses, restaurants, and more! Schedule a showing today and prepare to fall in love with your new home!
